"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## 介绍\\n\\nTokenized volatility protocol. Live on Ethereum, Arbitrum, and Polygon!\\n\\n一个代币化的波动率协议，支持ETH、Arbitrum、Polygon主网。\\n\\n投资结构豪华：Alameda Research、Three箭～～～\\n\\n**说明：ETH交互很贵，150u，最好用polygon或Arbitrum吧，泪奔～**\\n\\n官推：\\n\\n## 交互\\n\\n整个交互流程大概是，质押你的稳定币，去mint出波动率代币，然后使用这些波动率代币去参与投资，也可以组lp～\\n\\n**1、打开网站，链接钱包**\\n\\n目前支持Polygon、ETH和Arb了，我脑子抽了用ETH交互，不要学我\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/\\\\_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FKaSpkEcdYM3-ulcXzEa09.png\\\\&w=3840\\\\&q=90)\\n\\n**2、质押稳定币（本次以usdc为例），mint出波动率代币ETHV**\\n\\n![授权](https://mirror.xyz/\\\\_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FYOD3aNsCljYo6LBOzvuwC.png\\\\&w=3840\\\\&q=90)\\n\\n授权\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/\\\\_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FeCbXHYgTJ-mO0jCygRbsA.png\\\\&w=3840\\\\&q=90)\\n\\n等待mint成功～\\n\\n**3、点击顶部的Pool页面，进入流动池页面，提供ETHV/USDC流动性**\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/\\\\_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FpkGDM9hnVPlJ2Oh5vdeiG.png\\\\&w=3840\\\\&q=90)\\n\\n点击ETHV/USDC Uniswap v3 Pool，打开uniswap的流动池页面\\n\\n**点击Add Liquidity添加流动性**\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/\\\\_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FBZJ9gyhnMZo41i4VmJm6o.png\\\\&w=3840\\\\&q=90)\\n\\n提供流动性\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/\\\\_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FvNsaxZ977-s3WWyLeYalM.png\\\\&w=3840\\\\&q=90)\\n\\n交互完成，我好心疼。。。。\\n\\n算了下150u没了。。。。感觉要被反薅～～～\\n\\n**交互有问题的下面联系方式联系我。**\\n\\n**联系我：**\\n\\n**微博:**\\n\\n**推特：**\\n\",\"timestamp\":1639901917,\"title\":\"波动率指数协议volmex交互 — Mirror\"},\"digest\":\"q6sN2sV_ZL_b9DUi5Yl97PcgTGbFZG5p4J4EVrYJY9U\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x251CD9571c49C20dc3423681e67A72e4A59ACEc1\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"CaDQpwvcff4N-8IJFN1eQHVzQS0jxA_PI97-5SotxYI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"eh0FcWaawo2YkEzOKWCzF8gonrSQlBe-VNxDwW9APhg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Il2KaFxZSdVjAWysPVDePhg8un9TVZX7uhahB1cO-gpvE5jbVKdx7IjefCW3hoZ6P42OdCRz3yIAEJz7eRB-4w\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x7dfe7cc3e2a7c17f404ef35af6bbdfb51f3fca83049ce51f2672770c678f369e07011391fbc429fd62ba06cb7cdf90a5add5d653c7bddc5547e094bd2edb6bef1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"CaDQpwvcff4N-8IJFN1eQHVzQS0jxA_PI97-5SotxYI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"eh0FcWaawo2YkEzOKWCzF8gonrSQlBe-VNxDwW9APhg\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"q6sN2sV_ZL_b9DUi5Yl97PcgTGbFZG5p4J4EVrYJY9U\"}"